<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mars Mission</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; }
        img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .choices label { display: block; margin: 10px 0; font-size: 1.2em; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Mission: Identify the Camera</h1>
    <p>Study the image below, taken by the Curiosity Rover on Mars. Can you identify which camera captured this shot?</p>

    <img src="<%= missionPhoto.img_src %>" alt="Mission photo from Mars">

    <form action="/submit-mission" method="POST">
        <div class="choices">
            <% choices.forEach(choice => { %>
                <label>
                    <input type="radio" name="userAnswer" value="<%= choice %>" required>
                    <%= choice %>
                </label>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
        
        <input type="hidden" name="correctAnswer" value="<%= correctAnswer %>">
        <button type="submit" style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px;">Submit Intel</button>
    </form>

    <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><a href="/dashboard">Return to Dashboard</a></p>

</body>
</html> 